@jonatack 

Thanks a lot for reviewing!

All feedback addressed (+ added `using FopenFn` for readability): this PR should hopefully be ready for final review :)

Tested re-ACK 68afd3eeec27a270765ad26cd62d87cd0935e99f 

Nice improvement.

